Notes: Drury, ranked No. 5 in the WBCA/USA Today Div. II rankings, builds as much as
a 21-pt. lead (52-31) in the 2nd half...UMR closes to within eight at 57-49
with 3:50 to go, but the Lady Panthers outscore UMR 13-2 to finish the game.
UMR hosts Rockhurst Saturday at 1 p.m.
Game.Officials: Gus Lignoul,  Dennis Vacha,  David Thompson
